data.title: Jessica Pare Teeth: 'Mad Men' Star Discusses Her Famous Feature
data.meta_description: 'Mad Men' Star Talks About Her Famous Feature
data.text: "Weiner found himself drawn to Paré’s gap-toothed smile. Her teeth are so distinctive he even wrote a scene in which Megan recalls being told she could never be an actress because of them. Paré doesn’t understand all the fuss. 'I forget about them because they’re in my face and they do their job just great. I never get anything stuck in them.' (For the record, the camera must add ten pounds to each tooth, because in person she’s a knockout.)"
